  to: html
  output-file: index.html

  html-math-method: mathjax
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  css:

metadata
  crossref:
    chapters: true
  document-css: false
  link-citations: true
  date-format: long
  lang: en
  knitr:
    opts_chunk:
      comment: '#>'
      collapse: true
      cache: true
      width: 72

      fig.align: center
      fig.width: 6
      fig.height: 3.708
      fig.show: hold
      R.options:
        digits: 3
        width: 72
        formatR.indent: 2
        dplyr.summarise.inform: false
        dplyr.print_min: 5
        dplyr.print_max: 5
        ggrepel.max.overlaps: 100
  editor: visual
  theme: cosmo
  title: STAT 3000 Lecture Notes
  subtitle: Statistics with R Programming
